Class BiProduct<A,B>

java.lang.Object
civitas.celestis.util.product.BiProduct<A,B>
Type Parameters:
A - The type of the first product
B - The type of the second product
public class BiProduct<A,B> extends Object
This class is used to return two variables from a single method. null values are not supported.
